title: wiki: Minor typo on "Writing Web Applications"
body:
On https://golang.org/doc/articles/wiki/:

> With this web server running, a visit to `http://localhost:8080/view/test` should show a page titled `"test"` containing the words "Hello world".

This should be `http://localhost:8080/view/TestPage` and `"TestPage"` instead of `test`
